<item>
            <title>[LU-4793] CLIO per-page allocations use size-1024 slab</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4793</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running some simple read and write tests using &quot;dd&quot; to large files I see a huge amount of memory allocated by the size-1024 slab - about 1/4 if all RAM of the system.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The size of the per-page allocation must be reduced in some manner, since this is far to much memory wasted for CLIO overhead. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="23812">LU-4793</key>
            <summary>CLIO per-page allocations use size-1024 slab</summary>
